    <section class="section case-study" id="healthcare">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="case-study-content">
                <span class="case-study-tag">Healthcare</span>
                <div class="case-study-grid">
                    <div class="case-study-header">
                        <h2>Pharmacy AI Assistant</h2>
                        <p class="case-study-subtitle">How an AI-powered chatbot transformed customer engagement for a pharmacy chain.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="case-study-metrics">
                        <div class="metric">
                            <span class="metric-number">80%</span>
                            <span class="metric-label">Reduction in Response Time</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="metric">
                            <span class="metric-number">3x</span>
                            <span class="metric-label">Increase in Customer Engagement</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="metric">
                            <span class="metric-number">24/7</span>
                            <span class="metric-label">AI-Powered Customer Support</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="case-study-details">
                        <div class="case-block">
                            <h4>The Challenge</h4>
                            <p>A growing pharmacy chain was struggling with high customer inquiry volumes. Their team was overwhelmed with medication questions, prescription refill requests, and general inquiries. Customers often waited hours for responses, leading to frustration and lost business.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="case-block gold-bg">
                            <h4>The E³ Solution</h4>
                            <p>We built an intelligent AI chatbot integrated with WhatsApp and the pharmacy's website. The system could handle medication inquiries, process prescription refill requests, provide dosage information, and escalate complex questions to human pharmacists.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Natural language processing for medication queries</li>
                                <li>Automated prescription refill processing</li>
                                <li>24/7 availability</li>
                                <li>Seamless escalation to human support</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="case-block">
                            <h4>The Result</h4>
                            <p>Response time dropped from hours to seconds. Customer engagement increased threefold. The pharmacy team was freed from repetitive inquiries and could focus on high-value patient care. Customer satisfaction scores improved significantly.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="case-study-testimonial">
                        <span class="testimonial-quote">"</span>
                        <blockquote>
                            The AI system has revolutionized how we interact with our customers. We're now able to serve more people, faster, without compromising on quality.
                        </blockquote>
                        <cite>— Pharmacy Operations Manager</cite>
                    </div>

                    <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary case-cta">
                        <span class="btn-text">Build Your AI Solution</span>
                        <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

